/*****************************************************************
* Procedure Name:ANSI_Lookup_Claim
* Description:   
*
*		Name			Type		Description
*		---------		-------		----------------
* Params In:	-- HPF 13.0 ansi code
* Params Out: 
* Database: CABINET
* 
* NOTES: 
